The,TripExpert,Expert,Review,API,provides,developers,with,access,to,about,half,a,million,professional,reviews,for,hotels,restaurants,and,tourist,attractions,These,reviews,come,from,leading,travel,guides,magazines,and,newspapers,The,API,also,provides,users,with,access,to,TripExpert,Scores,which,are,generated,based,on,those,reviews,by,an,algorithm